data.description: Ready for a quick close. Gorgeous 2 BR 2.5 BA with loft and 1 car garage located in gated community with no CDD! Kitchen has 42'' cabinets, breakfast bar, and is open to the family room.  Large sliders providing lots of natural light lead to patio perfect for BBQing.  Wood laminate in the hallway and family room ceramic tile in kitchen, half bath, and foyer. Primary bedroom with full bath and walk-in closet, 2nd bedroom, guest full bath, a separate laundry room, and the loft area currently set up as bedroom are upstairs.  Community has pool and fitness room.  Bartram Park has great food and shopping and is close to Durbin Town Center.
